章10節)"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">我來，卻是為叫他們獲得生命，且獲得更豐富的生命。（若望福音10:10）</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">I have come so that they may have life, and have it to the full. (John 10:10)</div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-repeater-item-42c5aff swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="創世紀21章22節"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">在你所作的一切事上，天主常與你同在。（創世紀21:22）</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">God is with you in everything you do. (Genesis 21:22)</div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-repeater-item-050c44c swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="若望福音3章16節"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">天主竟這樣愛了世界，甚至賜下了自己的獨生子。（若望福音3:16）</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">For God so loved the world, he gave us his only begotten Son. (John 3:16)</div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-repeater-item-ab86c9f swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="德育活動(德訓篇37章17節)"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">你要保持良心提醒你的事，因為沒有比你的良心更忠實的。（德訓篇37:17）</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">Stick to the advice your own heart gives you, no one can be truer to you than that. (Ecclesiasticus 37:17)</div></div></div></div>				</div>
